[
    {
        "text": "The road ahead is not going to be easy.",
        "startTime": 49,
        "endTime": 2282,
        "slowStartTime": 223,
        "slowEndTime": 3648
    },
    {
        "text": "It never is, especially for folks like you and me.",
        "startTime": 3532,
        "endTime": 6681,
        "slowStartTime": 5448,
        "slowEndTime": 10247
    },
    {
        "text": "We've both felt the sting of those daily slights throughout our entire lives.",
        "startTime": 7348,
        "endTime": 12047,
        "slowStartTime": 11172,
        "slowEndTime": 18296
    },
    {
        "text": "The folks who crossed the street in fear of their safety.",
        "startTime": 12597,
        "endTime": 15481,
        "slowStartTime": 19045,
        "slowEndTime": 23447
    },
    {
        "text": "The clerks who kept a close eye on us in all those department stores.",
        "startTime": 15765,
        "endTime": 19559,
        "slowStartTime": 23797,
        "slowEndTime": 29563
    },
    {
        "text": "The people at formal events who assumed we were the help.",
        "startTime": 19899,
        "endTime": 22913,
        "slowStartTime": 29999,
        "slowEndTime": 34594
    },
    {
        "text": "And those who have questioned our intelligence, our honesty,...",
        "startTime": 23880,
        "endTime": 28315,
        "slowStartTime": 35970,
        "slowEndTime": 42697
    },
    {
        "text": "...even our love of this country.",
        "startTime": 28508,
        "endTime": 30652,
        "slowStartTime": 42912,
        "slowEndTime": 46203
    },
    {
        "text": "And I know that these little indignities are obviously nothing...",
        "startTime": 31807,
        "endTime": 35526,
        "slowStartTime": 47860,
        "slowEndTime": 53514
    },
    {
        "text": "...compared to what folks across the country are dealing with every single day.",
        "startTime": 35605,
        "endTime": 39601,
        "slowStartTime": 53557,
        "slowEndTime": 59626
    },
    {
        "text": "Those nagging worries that you're gonna get stopped...",
        "startTime": 40329,
        "endTime": 42629,
        "slowStartTime": 60643,
        "slowEndTime": 64168
    },
    {
        "text": "...or pulled over for absolutely no reason.",
        "startTime": 42734,
        "endTime": 45340,
        "slowStartTime": 64251,
        "slowEndTime": 68235
    },
    {
        "text": "The fear that your job application will be overlooked because of the way your name sounds.",
        "startTime": 45917,
        "endTime": 50629,
        "slowStartTime": 69025,
        "slowEndTime": 76168
    },
    {
        "text": "The agony of sending your kids to schools that may no longer be separate,...",
        "startTime": 51272,
        "endTime": 56327,
        "slowStartTime": 77058,
        "slowEndTime": 84716
    },
    {
        "text": "...but are far from equal.",
        "startTime": 56896,
        "endTime": 58078,
        "slowStartTime": 85494,
        "slowEndTime": 87342
    },
    {
        "text": "The realization that no matter how far you rise in life,...",
        "startTime": 59103,
        "endTime": 63612,
        "slowStartTime": 88805,
        "slowEndTime": 95643
    },
    {
        "text": "...how hard you work to be a good person, a good parent, a good citizen,...",
        "startTime": 64041,
        "endTime": 68779,
        "slowStartTime": 96212,
        "slowEndTime": 103394
    },
    {
        "text": "...for some folks, it will never be enough.",
        "startTime": 69065,
        "endTime": 72319,
        "slowStartTime": 103747,
        "slowEndTime": 108703
    },
    {
        "text": "But graduates, today I wanna be very clear that those feelings are not an excuse...",
        "startTime": 72809,
        "endTime": 81285,
        "slowStartTime": 109364,
        "slowEndTime": 122152
    },
    {
        "text": "...to just throw up our hands and give up.",
        "startTime": 81503,
        "endTime": 83802,
        "slowStartTime": 122404,
        "slowEndTime": 125928
    },
    {
        "text": "Not an excuse.",
        "startTime": 83930,
        "endTime": 84941,
        "slowStartTime": 126045,
        "slowEndTime": 127636
    },
    {
        "text": "They are not an excuse to lose hope.",
        "startTime": 85245,
        "endTime": 88292,
        "slowStartTime": 128018,
        "slowEndTime": 132663
    }
